title: Silver Needle
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2tjHybd

by NeyleiTarento

Jimin could say, that this business was the barista’s life. He looked like an art piece himself, he could just stand in the corner of the room with his stupidly broad shoulders and stupid rectangular smile and stupid sparkles in his brown eyes-

“Have you chosen yet?” came the stupidly low voice and Jimin almost jumped in his place from where he’s been staring at the pages.

“I’m more of a coffee type of guy. Tea isn’t exactly my cup of… tea.”

Basically, Jimin is an awkward shit that falls for a barista in a tea-house and shit goes down.
